- Prefer demonstrative schemes: arrows, formulas, before/after, small examples, role diagrams, question cards, and simple hand-drawn metaphors.
- Keep exact_text short. The image model must render it legibly inside the slide.
- Use Russian for exact_text. Do not include English visible text.
